<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.9">
<l>vāykoṇṭu māṉiṭam pāṭavan takavi yēṉallē</l>
<l>ṉāykoṇṭa cīrvaḷḷa lāḻippi rāṉeṉak kēyuḷaṉ</l>
<l>cāykoṇṭa vimmaiyuñ  cātittu vāṉavar nāṭṭaiyu</l>
<l>nīkaṇṭu koḷḷeṉṟu vīṭun taruniṉṟu niṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am not a poet who came to sing humanity with [his] mouth.</l>
<l>For me is the lord with the discus, the beautiful excellent liberal man.</l>
<l>Having established this brilliant birth, lasting, lasting he will give [me]</l>
<l>liberation, saying “see for yourself the land of the celestials”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
